      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky race to kick off the card with many of these babies at the races for the first time. Of the raced brigade EVER SO READY (1) has been right there in both Saturday outings this campaign and will appreciate the drop back in grade here. Ready to peak now third-up from the spell and looks the one they all have to run down. DOLLY BOOM (6) ran third in a rich Gold Coast contest on debut before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has since tuned up for this with a solid trial win and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. RUN LIKE A GIRL (8) is another resuming but showed enough when last in work to warrant consideration in a race of this calibre. In the mix. SETTLE THIS (5) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and any market support must be noted. The well-bred BERZELIUS (2) (out of dual-Listed winner Secret Liaison) next best out of the astute stable.",
